description: Bring HDMI capabilities to your smart phone or other mobile device with this Micro HDMI (Type D Connector) cable. Even with its small form factor, this cable supports the full HDMI specifications including: high speed 10.2 Gbps data rate, Ethernet over HDMI, 4k x 2k support, audio return channel, 3D and deep color support.  This is the newest and best digital video connection on the market. HDMI is the only cable that can transfer uncompressed high-definition video and multi channel digital audio in resolutions higher than 1440p. This CL2 rated(In Wall) cable will allow the transfer of digital audio and video in a single cable, permitting a less confusing mess of wires and a cleaner entertainment center. The HDMI connector is small, which makes it is ideal for installers and in-wall use. HDMI cables can be used with your HDTV's, DVD players, game consoles, cable and satellite set top boxes and DVRs. This cable conforms to the latest HDMI high speed with Ethernet specification.
title: C&E CNE25518 6-Feet High Speed with Ethernet HDMI to Micro HDMI Cable for HTC EVO 4G
